title: Seahawks-49ers MNF Preview, Lamar Jackson is the real deal (Football 11/11)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Jared Dubin to preview Seahawks vs 49ers on Monday Night Football (1:00). The guys discuss the current state of this rivalry, how injuries could impact the game, belief in Jimmy Garoppolo and Russell Wilson's MVP campaign. Then, Jason La Canfora joins the podcast to analyze Lamar Jackson's continued dominance (33:00), the Jets and Browns not being sold on their head coaches (42:30), Cam Newton's future in Carolina (53:00) and Jeff Bezos' interest in purchasing an NFL team (1:05:30).
